SUMMARY:Coworking Open House Week @ The Cloud Room
DTSTAMP:20260406T054319Z
DTSTART:20260416T160000Z
DESCRIPTION:Curious about coworking and looking for the perfect spot to get
	 work done and reach your goals? Join us for a complimentary day during ou
	r upcoming Open House Week and experience what it’s like to be a part of o
	ur incredible community!\n\nWhat's Included:\n\nOne Free Trial Day: Pick a
	ny day during Open House Week to try out our coworking space\, free of cha
	rge! Arrive anytime 9am or later — whatever works best with your schedule.
	\n\nAccess to our beautiful workspace including quiet desk space with moni
	tors\, large lounge area\, phone booths\, bar\, and outdoor patio.\n\nComp
	limentary coffee\, tea\, snacks and kombucha.\n\nHigh-speed Wi-Fi\, printi
	ng\, and meeting rooms available for rent\n\nThe chance to meet like-minde
	d professionals and get a feel for the Cloud Room vibe.\n\nSpecial Offer:\
	n\nIf you love your free day with us and decide to become a member\, we’ll
	 waive your initiation fees when you sign up! How to Join:\n\nReserve your
	 free trial day by selecting one day of your choice on our Calendly \\(one
	 free trial day per person\\)\n\nShow up and enjoy your day at Cloud Room!
	 Be sure to check in with the staff at the front of the lounge so we can g
	ive you a quick tour of the space and get you set up with the wifi.\n\nSig
	n up for membership to take advantage of waived initiation fees.\n\nDon’t 
	miss this chance to test out our space\, meet amazing people\, and see if 
	Cloud Room is the perfect fit for your work needs!\n\nCurrent Promotions:\
	n\n⭐️ Sign up for a grounded membership and get your first month free \\+ 1
	0% off you first year of membership. 3 month commitment required.\n\n⭐️ Flo
	ating Membership Promo: Take 50% off your first full month of floating mem
	bership.\n\nSpaces are limited—RSVP today.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com
	/events/#/details/coworking-open-house-week-the-cloud-room/18423258/2026-0
	4-16T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Food & Drink
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/coworking-open-house-week
	-the-cloud-room/18423258/2026-04-16T00
LOCATION:The Cloud Room\, 1424 11th Ave Suite 400\, Seattle\, WA
